\begin_layout Standard
This section investigates the effect of trade on wage inequality by exploration
 of theoretical models, as well as empirical evidence.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
MENTION GATT, EAST ASIA, URUGUAY ROUND, LATIN AMERICA AND OTHER COUNTRIES.
 
\end_layout

